# AI Agent Team — .gitignore  (scope: FRAMEWORK ONLY)
# Personal vault, private analytics data, large media, and secrets are excluded.
# IMPORTANT: gitignore comments must be on their OWN line — a trailing "# ..."
# after a pattern becomes part of the pattern and silently breaks it.

# --- Secrets (this tree is OneDrive-synced; never commit credentials) ---
.env
**/.env
*.key
*.pem
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- Personal / private content (not part of the shareable framework) ---
obsidian/
here/
fromtheinside/

# --- Private generated data (analytics, competitor/trend pulls, live numbers) ---
ig-dashboard/data/
intel/data/
intel/gdelt_5d.json
intel/radar-report.md
intel/trend-report.md
intel/viral-report.md
intel/news-report.md
intel/viral-teardown.md
team/stats.md
# auto-clip generated artifacts: transcripts/highlights are regenerable, clips are large
auto-clip/data/
auto-clip/out/
# self-improve generated grade ledger: regenerable from store.json by re-running grade.py
self-improve/data/

# --- Large media (110MB+ of May-14 TikTok analysis inputs) ---
*.mp4
*.wav
*.mov
*.mkv
frames/

# --- Archive / raw transcripts / obsolete one-offs ---
Ai agent team handoff.md
tiktok-analysis.md
/transcript.txt
/transcribe.py
compass_artifact_*.md
connect-instagram.ps1
FINISH-SETUP.md

# --- Tooling / OS junk ---
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log

# === 2026-06-28: keep the PUBLIC framework lean — commit source, not heavy/private outputs ===
# Carousel studio: keep build scripts + HTML + copy; drop rendered slides & AI asset images (regenerable)
carousel-builds/**/*.png
carousel-builds/**/*.jpg
carousel-builds/**/*.jpeg
carousel-builds/**/*.webp
carousel-builds/**/*.gif
# Color-engine LUTs: large (11MB each) + regenerable from the engine
**/input_luts/
**/resolve-luts/
# ClipWith edit: keep edit data (json/md/scripts/transcripts); drop heavy frames/graphics
clipwith-edit/reference-analysis/
clipwith-edit/graphics/
clipwith-edit/verify/
# Paid 3rd-party course material — do not redistribute on a public repo
gumroad/
# Private IG performance data & content playbook (mirrors the "Private generated data" block above)
ig-dashboard/3month-recap/
ig-dashboard/hook-bank.md
ig-dashboard/reach-recovery-plan.md
ig-dashboard/carousel-money-moves.md
# Saved-webpage junk ("Save Page As" dump of a Higgsfield assets page — scraped JS, not source)
carousel-builds/Assets • Higgsfield.html
carousel-builds/Assets • Higgsfield_files/
